"Suggested Citation: Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, National Center for Health Statistics. National Vital Statistics"
"System, Mortality 2018-2024 on CDC WONDER Online Database, released in 2026. Data are from the Multiple Cause of Death Files,"
"2018-2024, as compiled from data provided by the 57 vital statistics jurisdictions through the Vital Statistics Cooperative"
"Program. Accessed at http://wonder.cdc.gov/ucd-icd10-expanded.html on Jun 17, 2026 10:37:12 PM"
